      "writtenOn": "2016-09-23T19:14:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Alexei didn\u0027t care for the straight counts. I guess it should be CrashReportSetToPending, tracking the reason something got into kPending.\n\nHuh, that\u0027s interesting: https://cs.chromium.org/chromium/src/third_party/crashpad/crashpad/client/crash_report_database_win.cc?rcl\u003d0\u0026l\u003d798 Maybe we *do* retry on Windows?",
