        "id": 1144260
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-09-23T19:19:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ah, no, we don\u0027t. CallRecordUploadAttempt::Fire() makes this set it to kPending, but then immediately after we call SkipReportUpload(). That\u0027s a bit confusing, but I don\u0027t think there\u0027s unexpected retries. Well, UMA can confirm that for us anyway.",
      "parentUuid": "f076e782_17f82f62",
